Name: GREETING_NICE_3_MORNING
EN: "I love the smell of flowers in the morning!"
CY: "Dwi'n caru'r arogl y blodau yn y fore!"

Name: GREETING_NEUTRAL_3_MORNING
EN: "It's good to get out in the mornings, right?"
CY: "Mae'n iawn I fod tu mas yn y fore, reit?"

Name: GREETING_MEAN_3_MORNING
EN: "If you don’t have coffee I'm not interested"
CY: "Os does dim coffi gyda ti, sai'n diddoreb.."

Name: GREETING_NICE_1_AFTERNOON
CY: "Gobeithio eich bod wedi dod ag eli haul!"

Name: GREETING_NICE_2_AFTERNOON
EN: "I love the sun at this time of day!"
CY: "Dwi'n caru'r haul yr adeg hon o'r dydd!"

Name: GREETING_NICE_1_NIGHT
EN: "It's nice to see you this evening!"

Name: GREETING_NICE_2_NIGHT
EN: "I love how the moon looks tonight!"
CY: "Dwi wrth fy modd gyda sut mae'r lleuad yn edrych heno!"

Name: GREETING_MEAN_3_NIGHT
EN: "Had enough of you for one day"
CY: "Wedi cael digon ohonoch chi am un diwrnod"

Name: RESPONSE_MEAN_1_NIGHT
EN: "Wake up in a better mood yeah?"

Name: INTRO_SHOPKEEP
EN: "Welcome to the island shop! What can I get you?"
CY: "Croeso i siop yr ynys! Beth allai fi cael i chi?"

Name: SHOP_CLOSED
EN: Sorry, the shop is not open at night
CY: Sori, Dyw'r siop ddim yn agor trwy'r nos
